Dialogue: 0.0:09:50.13.0:09:52.50.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Feelings? What do you mean?  - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:52.60.0:09:53.67.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Like intense butterflies.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:53.77.0:09:54.73.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Right?  - No. I get that.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:54.83.0:09:57.14.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..but it wasn't your first time.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:57.24.0:09:58.50.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I don't know.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:58.60.0:10:01.21.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..So you're saying Charlie is your first...
Dialogue: 0.0:10:01.31.0:10:02.94.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Love... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:03.04.0:10:05.44.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Your first love or your first crush?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:07.68.0:10:08.88.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Both. I think.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:09.75.0:10:11.58.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- What. is that insane?  - At 30?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:11.68.0:10:14.29.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Well. I mean. I was 28 when we met. so...
Dialogue: 0.0:10:14.39.0:10:15.35.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Still!
Dialogue: 0.0:10:16.59.0:10:18.59.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I don't know. I used to be ugly.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:18.69.0:10:20.12.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Oh. come on!
Dialogue: 0.0:10:20.86.0:10:22.26.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Don't freak out.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:22.36.0:10:23.93.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..but there's a giant spider
Dialogue: 0.0:10:24.03.0:10:26.73.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..that's crawling up your back and it's almost into your hair.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:26.83.0:10:28.17.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Just don't panic.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:31.67.0:10:32.60.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Nothing?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:32.71.0:10:33.97.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- No.  - No.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:34.07.0:10:36.07.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I feel like you just have to do it louder.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:40.28.0:10:42.25.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Okay. Um...
Dialogue: 0.0:10:42.35.0:10:44.95.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I love you so much it hurts.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:45.92.0:10:47.42.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I can't be without you.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:48.75.0:10:50.76.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It's scary 'cause I can't imagine...
Dialogue: 0.0:10:56.83.0:11:00.37.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I want to marry you but I'm too afraid to even ask.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:03.90.0:11:05.24.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I think I caught that.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:06.71.0:11:07.87.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You did?
Dialogue: 0.0:11:08.71.0:11:09.87.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..A hairy knife?
Dialogue: 0.0:11:10.34.0:11:11.34.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..A what?
Dialogue: 0.0:11:11.44.0:11:13.28.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Did you say something about. like. a hairy knife?
Dialogue: 0.0:11:14.51.0:11:16.05.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- No.  - No?
Dialogue: 0.0:11:17.05.0:11:18.22.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Emma. that's not even a thing.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:22.15.0:11:23.39.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:11:23.49.0:11:25.92.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah. No. it's good.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:26.02.0:11:27.99.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Oh. come on. you gotta be a bit more specific than that.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:28.09.0:11:29.19.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah. it's a little corny
Dialogue: 0.0:11:29.29.0:11:31.76.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..in a wedding speech kind of way. but it's. um...
Dialogue: 0.0:11:31.86.0:11:34.27.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..All the pieces are there. you know.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:34.37.0:11:35.03.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I think you have it.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:36.67.0:11:37.84.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..All right. you can't cry
Dialogue: 0.0:11:37.94.0:11:39.44.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..and say it sucks.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:45.01.0:11:46.88.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And looking at each other.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:59.86.0:12:01.03.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Nice.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:06.46.0:12:09.27.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Slide... and two.
