Dialogue: 0.0:12:14.37.0:12:15.34.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Nice.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:18.98.0:12:21.45.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And kiss. Great.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:24.02.0:12:25.82.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Ready and drag.
