Dialogue: 0.0:12:59.69.0:13:01.05.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Oh.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:01.15.0:13:02.76.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Oh?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:02.86.0:13:04.49.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Good.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:04.59.0:13:07.96.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And this time. Emma. go around a full circle.
