Dialogue: 0.0:13:17.84.0:13:19.07.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And turn.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:19.64.0:13:20.64.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And step.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:21.41.0:13:22.74.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And turn.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:22.84.0:13:24.21.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And step.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:25.81.0:13:30.18.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Ready and drag. step. step. in.
