Dialogue: 0.0:13:33.46.0:13:34.46.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Good.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:44.31.0:13:45.14.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Oh.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:45.24.0:13:47.14.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Nearly there.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:47.24.0:13:48.78.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Okay. not bad.  - Okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:48.88.0:13:50.61.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Not bad.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:50.71.0:13:52.68.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Still a little difficulty in the middle section.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:52.78.0:13:54.12.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..but overall much better.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:54.22.0:13:55.48.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Yeah.  - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:55.58.0:13:56.85.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Let's just do it again?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:56.95.0:13:58.39.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Okay.  - Okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:58.95.0:14:00.12.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:01.86.0:14:03.09.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I just... I don't know.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:03.19.0:14:04.49.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I feel like we should just dance normally. right?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:04.59.0:14:05.63.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:05.73.0:14:07.53.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Well. just the...
Dialogue: 0.0:14:07.63.0:14:10.40.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I don't know. it kinda feels a little performative.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:10.50.0:14:13.00.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It's a wedding. It's performative by nature.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:13.10.0:14:14.80.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah. I think if we just do it...
Dialogue: 0.0:14:14.90.0:14:16.20.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0.....a couple more times.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:16.30.0:14:17.71.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I'm gonna get it perfect. I swear.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:17.81.0:14:19.81.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I can't make up new choreography right on the spot.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:19.91.0:14:21.14.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:21.24.0:14:23.71.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Okay. well. just hear me out.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:23.81.0:14:25.45.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Hear me out. Please. Please.  - No. Emma. Please.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:25.55.0:14:27.85.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Please. please. please.  - Emma.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:34.56.0:14:36.49.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What's this?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:36.59.0:14:38.76.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..She puts this on when I'm in a bad mood
Dialogue: 0.0:14:38.86.0:14:40.26.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..just to fuck with me.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:43.46.0:14:46.00.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You like this song. You do.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:46.10.0:14:48.20.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- You fucking dance.  - No.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:48.30.0:14:49.60.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Dance with me.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:49.71.0:14:50.77.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Come on.  - No.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:50.87.0:14:53.07.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yes. it's cute. Yes.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:54.28.0:14:56.08.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Hey. can we stop fucking around?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:56.18.0:14:57.68.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What the fuck was that about?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:58.85.0:15:00.48.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It's like why does she care so much?
Dialogue: 0.0:15:01.58.0:15:02.42.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..She just doesn't like it
Dialogue: 0.0:15:02.52.0:15:03.65.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..when you don't take her seriously enough.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:03.75.0:15:06.09.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Shut up. You know what I mean!
Dialogue: 0.0:15:06.19.0:15:08.92.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You know. she's just like so intense.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:09.02.0:15:10.32.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Uh-huh.  - And she doesn't smile.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:10.42.0:15:13.39.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Like. I've literally never seen her smile.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:13.49.0:15:15.50.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0.."It's performative by nature."
Dialogue: 0.0:15:17.50.0:15:18.50.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What?
Dialogue: 0.0:15:20.30.0:15:21.67.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I think that was Pauline.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:22.44.0:15:23.44.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Oh. where?
Dialogue: 0.0:15:23.54.0:15:25.11.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Um...
Dialogue: 0.0:15:25.21.0:15:28.11.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..She's on the corner. like. smoking heroin.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:28.94.0:15:31.58.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Wait. Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0.0:15:32.51.0:15:33.25.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:33.35.0:15:34.72.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Wait. like our Pauline?
Dialogue: 0.0:15:34.82.0:15:35.82.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:36.79.0:15:39.49.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..No. I mean. it's probably not.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:40.25.0:15:42.79.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- That's her. Uh...  - Okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:42.89.0:15:44.29.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Look. Go look.  - Okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:53.74.0:15:56.04.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It was her. It was the fucking wedding DJ.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:56.14.0:15:58.27.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- You're kidding!  - Are you sure it was heroin?
Dialogue: 0.0:15:58.37.0:16:00.01.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Well. we can't prove it was heroin.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:00.11.0:16:01.71.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It was like she was smoking a thing
Dialogue: 0.0:16:01.81.0:16:03.81.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..out of. like. a piece of foil.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:03.91.0:16:05.05.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah. yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:05.15.0:16:06.58.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Like. what else could that possibly be?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:06.68.0:16:07.42.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Did you talk to her?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:07.52.0:16:08.88.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..No. no. She didn't see us.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:08.98.0:16:10.35.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Wait. what are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:10.45.0:16:12.25.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I don't know. I think we just get somebody else. I guess.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:12.35.0:16:13.79.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..The wedding is this Saturday.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:13.89.0:16:15.52.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Well. we just get. like. a playlist or something. no?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:15.62.0:16:17.63.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..No. You need a DJ. trust me.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:17.73.0:16:18.66.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Who did yours again?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:18.76.0:16:20.36.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..No one. It was a disaster.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:20.46.0:16:21.96.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Are you just afraid you're not gonna find someone else?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:22.06.0:16:24.20.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..No. I just... I don't know. It's not a deal-breaker. right?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:24.30.0:16:26.70.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Like. people do drugs. It's...
Dialogue: 0.0:16:26.80.0:16:29.50.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Babe. there's drugs and then there's heroin.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:29.97.0:16:31.31.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..That's the line?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:31.41.0:16:34.64.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..She's not performing surgery. She's. like. a... She's a DJ.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:34.74.0:16:36.18.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..But isn't it more the fact
Dialogue: 0.0:16:36.28.0:16:37.71.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..that she was doin' it out in the street?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:37.81.0:16:39.95.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Doesn't that say something about where she's at in life?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:40.05.0:16:42.08.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Okay. she wasn't. like. "on the street."
Dialogue: 0.0:16:42.18.0:16:43.55.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It was like...
Dialogue: 0.0:16:43.65.0:16:45.59.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It was like a party or something.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:45.69.0:16:47.29.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..There was a whole bunch of other crackheads.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:47.39.0:16:49.59.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Why are you trying to be her publicist all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:49.69.0:16:51.19.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I don't know. I just don't wanna dismiss her
Dialogue: 0.0:16:51.29.0:16:52.39.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..'cause of this one thing. You know?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:52.49.0:16:55.90.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Just checking in. How was that mushroom risotto?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:56.00.0:16:57.77.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- It was so good.  - It was really. really good.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:57.87.0:16:59.03.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Yeah.  - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:59.13.0:17:01.40.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You need more time to think or can we commit?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:01.50.0:17:03.01.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Do you wanna... Let's commit.  - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:03.11.0:17:04.81.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Aw.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:04.91.0:17:06.27.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yes. we commit to it.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:06.37.0:17:07.41.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- We'll commit to it.  - Just so you know.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:07.51.0:17:10.75.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..it kinda has to be final this time. so...
Dialogue: 0.0:17:10.85.0:17:12.98.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Oh. yeah. yeah. Yeah. we totally get it. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:13.08.0:17:14.35.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And. um. can I ask. is there any way
Dialogue: 0.0:17:14.45.0:17:16.48.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..of getting another glass of the skin contact?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:16.58.0:17:19.72.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..'Cause I haven't quite made my mind up about the wine yet.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:19.82.0:17:21.82.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Okay.  - Yeah. me too. actually. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:21.92.0:17:23.62.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Mike.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:28.23.0:17:29.20.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..We're not a bar.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:29.30.0:17:30.63.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Cheers!
Dialogue: 0.0:17:30.73.0:17:33.30.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Love you guys.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:33.40.0:17:35.37.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You know. I barely touched the food at our wedding.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:35.47.0:17:37.04.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Too much adrenaline.  - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:37.14.0:17:38.34.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And then we ran around at 2:00 a.m.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:38.44.0:17:40.41.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..looking for a slice of pizza.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:41.58.0:17:43.18.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..We should go to the diner.
