Dialogue: 0.0:43:13.64.0:43:15.47.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You probably noticed them. They're a little loud. but...
Dialogue: 0.0:43:21.91.0:43:23.78.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Did you actually like the lilies?
Dialogue: 0.0:43:25.72.0:43:27.35.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..'Cause I can call him back if you didn't.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:28.95.0:43:31.42.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Uh. no. it's fine. Yeah.  - Okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:32.82.0:43:33.99.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:43:37.66.0:43:38.93.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..How close did you get?
Dialogue: 0.0:43:39.03.0:43:40.87.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You probably wanna know why.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:42.80.0:43:44.00.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0.."Why'd she do it?
Dialogue: 0.0:43:44.80.0:43:46.14.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0.."What's wrong with her?"
Dialogue: 0.0:43:51.68.0:43:52.94.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What the fuck.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:02.35.0:44:03.52.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Hey. fucker.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:04.39.0:44:05.92.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Hey. fucker.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:06.02.0:44:07.99.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You wanna fucking die?
Dialogue: 0.0:44:16.37.0:44:17.37.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Hi.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:18.17.0:44:19.14.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..By the time you see this.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:19.24.0:44:21.34.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I'll most likely already be gone.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:22.94.0:44:24.54.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And now you're wondering why.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:25.68.0:44:26.91.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0.."Why did she..."
Dialogue: 0.0:44:28.05.0:44:29.21.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Fuck.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:36.85.0:44:38.32.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Oh. my God. There's a shooting.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:38.42.0:44:40.29.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- What?  - Yeah. at the mall.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:42.36.0:44:43.63.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..People are. like. jumping out of windows and shit.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:43.73.0:44:44.70.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What? Right now?
Dialogue: 0.0:44:44.80.0:44:46.67.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Oh. my God. I was just there.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:46.77.0:44:47.90.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What the fuck is going on?
Dialogue: 0.0:44:48.00.0:44:49.37.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..There was another mass shooting?
Dialogue: 0.0:44:49.47.0:44:51.54.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Technically. it wasn't a mass shooting. but yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:52.57.0:44:53.84.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0.0:44:53.94.0:44:56.97.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Only three people died. It has to be four or more.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:57.81.0:45:00.75.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Uh-huh. okay. Uh...
Dialogue: 0.0:45:01.58.0:45:04.02.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}And that's the reason you didn't do it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:45:04.12.0:45:06.08.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}'Cause someone else...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:45:06.18.0:45:08.45.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..That's the reason you didn't do it. 'cause...
Dialogue: 0.0:45:09.35.0:45:10.62.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..somebody else just got there first?
Dialogue: 0.0:45:13.06.0:45:16.70.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I just got the news that Marcus didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:16.80.0:45:17.83.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What?
Dialogue: 0.0:45:17.93.0:45:19.46.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..He passed away earlier today...
Dialogue: 0.0:45:19.56.0:45:21.60.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0.....at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:24.97.0:45:26.44.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}Who the fuck does something like that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:45:26.54.0:45:30.41.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Like. what is wrong with you? You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0.0:45:30.51.0:45:31.88.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:34.75.0:45:36.98.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah. It's like...
Dialogue: 0.0:45:37.82.0:45:40.18.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..how can someone even. like...
Dialogue: 0.0:45:41.19.0:45:43.05.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Get the idea?  - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:43.15.0:45:45.76.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0.....with being here with each other
Dialogue: 0.0:45:45.86.0:45:47.16.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..in a moment like this.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:47.26.0:45:49.66.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..and really seeing each other. really hearing each other.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:49.76.0:45:51.00.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..feeling each other.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:52.96.0:45:54.47.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Some of us might be scared.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:55.60.0:45:57.50.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Some of us might be angry.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:57.60.0:46:00.04.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I bet some of us are confused today. aren't we?
Dialogue: 0.0:46:01.57.0:46:03.31.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}That's okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:46:03.41.0:46:05.61.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..We ain't gonna run away from those feelings today.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:07.15.0:46:08.05.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..So here's what we're gonna do.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:08.15.0:46:09.68.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I wanna try an exercise with y'all.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:09.78.0:46:12.92.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..All right. everybody get up on your feet real quick.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:14.05.0:46:15.02.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What I want you to do
Dialogue: 0.0:46:15.12.0:46:17.46.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..is to start slowly walking around.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:19.56.0:46:21.39.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Good.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:21.49.0:46:25.63.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Now. after a moment. I want you to stop.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:25.73.0:46:29.27.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Okay. look at that person that's right in front of you.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:30.50.0:46:31.34.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..See if you can sense
Dialogue: 0.0:46:31.44.0:46:34.24.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..what they're experiencing right now.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:34.34.0:46:36.61.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}Yeah. okay. Any other thoughts?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:46:36.71.0:46:38.88.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I don't know. I just feel like this is specifically
Dialogue: 0.0:46:38.98.0:46:41.05.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..a male problem. right?
Dialogue: 0.0:46:41.15.0:46:43.58.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Like it's always some angry. crazy guy.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:44.25.0:46:46.65.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Emma?  - Hm?
Dialogue: 0.0:46:46.75.0:46:48.09.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You don't agree?
Dialogue: 0.0:46:48.19.0:46:49.65.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..No. there's been a few.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:50.09.0:46:51.29.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..A few what?
Dialogue: 0.0:46:51.99.0:46:54.43.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Mass shootings by women.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:54.53.0:46:56.33.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Well. not in America.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:56.43.0:46:58.00.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah. I mean. there's even that song.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:58.10.0:46:59.73.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- {\c&H38d832&\i1}I Don't Like Mondays.{\i0}{\c}  - What?
Dialogue: 0.0:46:59.83.0:47:00.90.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It's about a woman
Dialogue: 0.0:47:01.00.0:47:02.10.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..who shot a bunch of people from her window
Dialogue: 0.0:47:02.20.0:47:03.87.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..because she hated Mondays.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:03.97.0:47:07.31.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It's not just men. and they're not all crazy.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:07.41.0:47:09.51.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..A lot of them are shockingly normal.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:09.61.0:47:10.64.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Normal?
Dialogue: 0.0:47:10.74.0:47:12.74.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I mean. like. what the hell are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0.0:47:12.85.0:47:14.95.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}Look them in the eyes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:47:15.05.0:47:17.58.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Acknowledge them. Be with them.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:17.68.0:47:18.65.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Be aware of them.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:20.92.0:47:22.62.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It's okay if you're emotional.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:25.12.0:47:28.49.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Okay. let's keep doing it. Keep walking. Keep going.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:28.59.0:47:31.40.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}So. uh. I was gonna ask you if you wanted to join me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:47:31.50.0:47:34.13.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..and. you know. try to do something.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:35.67.0:47:36.60.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..About?
Dialogue: 0.0:47:36.70.0:47:38.07.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Gun violence.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:38.57.0:47:39.34.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Oh.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:39.44.0:47:40.77.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..'Cause I'm just trying to organize
Dialogue: 0.0:47:40.87.0:47:42.14.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..a little something. you know?
Dialogue: 0.0:47:42.24.0:47:44.91.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Unless you. like. love guns or something.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:45.01.0:47:47.14.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah. no.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:47.25.0:47:49.21.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It's kind of like that Louis Malle movie.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:49.95.0:47:51.18.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What?
Dialogue: 0.0:47:51.28.0:47:53.22.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Do you know the one about the guy who wants to join
Dialogue: 0.0:47:53.32.0:47:54.72.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..the French Resistance.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:54.82.0:47:57.79.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..but they reject him. so he joins the Nazis instead?
Dialogue: 0.0:47:59.49.0:48:01.13.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..But it's. like. the other way around.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:03.03.0:48:04.43.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I haven't seen that one.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:04.53.0:48:06.50.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I don't know. if anyone wants to volunteer?
Dialogue: 0.0:48:07.90.0:48:09.27.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What about Emma?
Dialogue: 0.0:48:09.90.0:48:11.24.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Me?  - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:11.34.0:48:13.64.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I mean. I feel like you'd be a good speaker.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:13.74.0:48:14.64.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Why?
Dialogue: 0.0:48:14.74.0:48:17.64.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I don't know. I mean. it just makes sense.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:17.74.0:48:19.34.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I mean. you sound legit.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:19.44.0:48:21.38.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..and I just feel like you have the best face for it.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:23.68.0:48:25.25.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Okay. Yeah. Emma it is.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:36.76.0:48:37.70.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}Okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:48:37.80.0:48:39.53.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}Let's make the world a better place. right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:48:40.54.0:48:43.51.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..No more guns! No more guns!
Dialogue: 0.0:48:47.05.0:48:48.58.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And you didn't feel like a fraud?
Dialogue: 0.0:48:49.65.0:48:50.62.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..No.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:50.72.0:48:53.32.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It felt like finally waking up from a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:55.06.0:48:56.26.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Just like that?
Dialogue: 0.0:48:56.93.0:48:58.23.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I mean. I guess.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:00.63.0:49:01.63.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:03.26.0:49:06.40.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And you never had those issues again?
Dialogue: 0.0:49:06.50.0:49:08.20.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Like what? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0.0:49:08.87.0:49:09.87.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Like...
Dialogue: 0.0:49:10.91.0:49:12.81.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..violent urges...
Dialogue: 0.0:49:12.91.0:49:14.11.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..God. no. No.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:14.21.0:49:15.61.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:17.38.0:49:18.38.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..But. like. when did...
Dialogue: 0.0:49:18.48.0:49:20.18.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Charlie. can we stop talking about this?
Dialogue: 0.0:49:22.32.0:49:23.95.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Just... Until after the wedding?
Dialogue: 0.0:49:24.05.0:49:27.32.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Because... I just... I don't... I don't wanna ruin everything.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:27.42.0:49:29.79.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And I don't want you to look at me differently.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:29.89.0:49:32.76.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And I just... I love you. I love you so much.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:38.13.0:49:39.30.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I love you too.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:44.11.0:49:45.64.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Rachel's not responding.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:46.31.0:49:47.71.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It's pretty late.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:47.81.0:49:51.35.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah. well. she's not responding to my emails either.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:51.45.0:49:52.81.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Why are you emailing her?
Dialogue: 0.0:49:52.91.0:49:55.48.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..'Cause I stupidly got Alice to hire her for this work thing.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:56.18.0:49:57.42.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I'll just call Mike in the morning.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:57.52.0:49:59.15.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..They probably both hate me.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:01.29.0:50:02.39.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..They don't hate you.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:02.49.0:50:04.33.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It's gonna be all right. I promise.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:04.43.0:50:05.99.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0.0:50:06.09.0:50:07.60.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..'Cause it's just Rachel. She's just...
Dialogue: 0.0:50:07.70.0:50:10.90.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..She's just overreacting. like she always does.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:25.58.0:50:26.55.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You know...
Dialogue: 0.0:50:27.08.0:50:28.28.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What?
Dialogue: 0.0:50:32.05.0:50:34.36.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Freud said something like. uh.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:34.46.0:50:37.96.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..the feelings that we don't talk about get buried alive.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:38.06.0:50:40.46.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..only to come out in uglier ways.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:43.40.0:50:45.70.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Is that what you feel right now?
Dialogue: 0.0:50:47.84.0:50:51.41.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}No. I just think it's important to talk.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:50:52.01.0:50:52.97.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}Yeah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:50:54.68.0:50:55.78.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}And we did.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:50:58.51.0:50:59.72.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}We did. yeah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:51:01.95.0:51:03.79.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}And we're okay. right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:51:06.49.0:51:08.02.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}Yeah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:52:04.71.0:52:06.21.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Morning.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:06.31.0:52:08.02.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Morning. How'd you sleep?
Dialogue: 0.0:52:08.12.0:52:09.32.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Not great.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:10.72.0:52:12.85.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What... What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0.0:52:12.95.0:52:15.89.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Just working on my speech.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:19.73.0:52:21.63.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- I'm just gonna have a shower.  - Okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:22.96.0:52:24.77.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Hey.  - Hm?
Dialogue: 0.0:52:24.87.0:52:25.83.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Kiss.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:01.60.0:53:02.87.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Hey. Charlie. did you...
Dialogue: 0.0:53:04.37.0:53:06.37.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Jesus. you scared me.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:06.47.0:53:07.98.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I was making a smoothie.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:10.31.0:53:11.98.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Why are you looking at me like that?
Dialogue: 0.0:53:12.08.0:53:13.08.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Like what?
Dialogue: 0.0:53:14.25.0:53:15.88.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Like you're scared of me.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:15.98.0:53:18.02.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It was just like a... It was a reflex.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:20.59.0:53:22.86.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Do you think I came in here to stab you?
Dialogue: 0.0:53:24.29.0:53:27.39.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..No. What? Of course not. I...
Dialogue: 0.0:53:28.00.0:53:29.06.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What was the question?
Dialogue: 0.0:53:42.34.0:53:43.51.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Very funny.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:48.65.0:53:50.95.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Didn't you say you had a friend that died?
Dialogue: 0.0:53:51.05.0:53:51.85.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What?
Dialogue: 0.0:53:51.95.0:53:53.42.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Like. when you were younger.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:53.52.0:53:55.49.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..In a car accident or something?
Dialogue: 0.0:53:58.09.0:53:59.96.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Uh. yeah. My neighbor.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:01.26.0:54:02.50.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Were you guys close?
Dialogue: 0.0:54:02.60.0:54:05.67.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..No. not really. She was a couple of years older than me.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:06.80.0:54:09.04.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And how old was she when it happened?
Dialogue: 0.0:54:09.14.0:54:10.07.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..She was. like. 12.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:10.17.0:54:12.44.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..No shit. Wow.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:12.54.0:54:14.44.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..That must have been a really crazy thing to witness.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:14.54.0:54:16.18.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..like. at that age.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:16.28.0:54:18.78.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I didn't actually witness it.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:18.88.0:54:22.42.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..No. but still. You never had therapy or anything?
Dialogue: 0.0:54:22.52.0:54:23.95.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I was 10.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:24.05.0:54:26.69.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah. but. like. 10 is a very vulnerable age...
Dialogue: 0.0:54:26.79.0:54:28.39.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Okay. Charlie. please.  - What?
Dialogue: 0.0:54:28.52.0:54:29.66.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I just... I know what you're trying to say.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:29.76.0:54:32.29.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..and I don't think it's relevant.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:32.39.0:54:33.56.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..How do you know if it's relevant or not
Dialogue: 0.0:54:33.66.0:54:35.06.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..if you haven't analyzed it?
Dialogue: 0.0:54:37.60.0:54:39.03.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Sure.  - Right?
Dialogue: 0.0:54:40.63.0:54:41.97.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..So. three o'clock. then?
Dialogue: 0.0:54:43.34.0:54:44.24.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- What?  - For City Hall.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:44.34.0:54:46.17.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..for the marriage license.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:46.27.0:54:47.98.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Oh. yeah. Um. yes.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:37.66.0:55:38.99.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Oh. fuck. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:39.09.0:55:40.30.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Sorry. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:40.40.0:55:41.70.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Jesus.  - Um...
Dialogue: 0.0:55:41.80.0:55:42.53.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Hey.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:42.63.0:55:44.07.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Uh. have you talked to Rachel?
Dialogue: 0.0:55:45.10.0:55:46.60.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..No. I have not.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:46.70.0:55:48.54.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Oh. um. would you mind just nudging her?
Dialogue: 0.0:55:48.64.0:55:50.04.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I just haven't heard from her.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:51.94.0:55:54.34.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Misha. what is this?
Dialogue: 0.0:55:54.44.0:55:55.71.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Did you put this on my desk?
Dialogue: 0.0:55:56.21.0:55:57.21.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..No.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:58.08.0:55:59.35.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Do you know who did?
Dialogue: 0.0:55:59.45.0:56:00.68.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..No.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:01.78.0:56:03.82.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It didn't just come in the mail?
Dialogue: 0.0:56:04.95.0:56:05.72.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:56:05.82.0:56:07.62.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah. Sorry. what did you want?
Dialogue: 0.0:56:07.72.0:56:10.52.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Just an update. She's just. like. not responding.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:11.99.0:56:15.00.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I think... I think she's just. like. really busy.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:15.10.0:56:16.46.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Doesn't need to be right now.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:16.56.0:56:18.47.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah. But she's. like. always busy.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:18.57.0:56:21.04.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Like. juggling a million things.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:21.14.0:56:23.57.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What does that mean? She's not gonna do it?
Dialogue: 0.0:56:23.67.0:56:27.51.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I mean... probably not.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:27.61.0:56:29.98.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..But this was your idea.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:30.08.0:56:33.11.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah. but she kind of talked me into it. you know?
Dialogue: 0.0:56:33.21.0:56:35.25.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..She's in marketing. She's just very good at that.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:35.35.0:56:37.32.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:37.42.0:56:40.19.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Okay. So. what should we do?
Dialogue: 0.0:56:42.56.0:56:44.13.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I mean. honestly. I think
Dialogue: 0.0:56:44.23.0:56:47.30.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..we just. like. move on with someone else. 'cause...
Dialogue: 0.0:56:48.00.0:56:49.10.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..She's great. Like. don't get me wrong.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:49.20.0:56:51.70.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It's just. she sucks at time management.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:52.53.0:56:53.50.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:53.60.0:56:55.90.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Sorry.  - She's your friend.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:58.88.0:58:00.88.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Is... Is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:58:02.21.0:58:03.21.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah. I'm just...
Dialogue: 0.0:58:04.72.0:58:05.88.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What?
Dialogue: 0.0:58:07.35.0:58:09.92.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Nothing.  - Okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:58:11.89.0:58:14.59.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Do you... Do you need some help? Or...
Dialogue: 0.0:58:14.69.0:58:16.16.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..No. just. like...
Dialogue: 0.0:58:18.56.0:58:19.73.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:58:28.41.0:58:29.37.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Hm...
Dialogue: 0.0:58:37.98.0:58:41.49.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Um. Charlie. we don't have to do this if you don't want to.
Dialogue: 0.0:58:41.59.0:58:44.22.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..No. I do. I do. I do. Just...
Dialogue: 0.0:58:44.32.0:58:45.69.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Just give me a second.
Dialogue: 0.0:58:45.79.0:58:46.96.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:58:51.93.0:58:55.93.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Okay. I feel like... You have to stop thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0.0:58:56.03.0:58:57.10.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Hey. come on.
Dialogue: 0.0:58:57.20.0:58:58.50.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You can't just say. "Stop thinking about it."
Dialogue: 0.0:58:58.60.0:58:59.60.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..So. you are thinking about it?
Dialogue: 0.0:58:59.70.0:59:00.97.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I'm not thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0.0:59:03.24.0:59:05.48.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..For fuck's sakes. I am thinking about it now.
Dialogue: 0.0:59:07.28.0:59:08.71.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Let's just start over.
Dialogue: 0.0:59:25.96.0:59:27.97.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  When you're sitting on your own  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:59:28.07.0:59:34.31.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  And you feel the city life surround you  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:59:34.41.0:59:37.24.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  And she's always on the phone and...  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:59:37.34.0:59:38.51.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Is that seat taken?
Dialogue: 0.0:59:41.48.0:59:42.75.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0.0:59:52.39.0:59:53.83.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Do you live around here?
Dialogue: 0.0:59:55.33.0:59:56.86.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What?
Dialogue: 0.0:59:56.96.0:59:58.90.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It's just that you look familiar.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:00.87.1:00:03.97.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Um. yeah. I'm...
Dialogue: 0.1:00:04.07.1:00:05.47.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah. I live near here.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:05.57.1:00:06.77.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Oh. cool.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:07.64.1:00:08.94.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I'm Emma. by the way.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:09.71.1:00:10.91.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What's your name?
Dialogue: 0.1:00:13.28.1:00:15.91.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- I don't think this is gonna...  - I'm sorry. what's your name?
Dialogue: 0.1:00:19.88.1:00:22.25.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Charlie.  - Charlie.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:23.49.1:00:24.46.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What's a...
Dialogue: 0.1:00:25.39.1:00:28.06.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..sexy guy like you doing out all alone?
Dialogue: 0.1:00:29.73.1:00:30.83.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Emma. look...
Dialogue: 0.1:00:30.93.1:00:34.30.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Do you have an accent? What's that? Australian?
Dialogue: 0.1:00:34.40.1:00:35.40.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..This isn't gonna work.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:35.50.1:00:37.17.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What's not gonna work?
Dialogue: 0.1:00:37.27.1:00:38.80.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Look. let's just not do this.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:38.90.1:00:40.67.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Do what?  - Just stop. Stop.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:40.77.1:00:41.74.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..This is stupid.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:41.84.1:00:43.27.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Like. I'm not overthinking anything.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:43.37.1:00:45.88.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It's just been a stressful week. I...
Dialogue: 0.1:00:45.98.1:00:47.88.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I don't even care about it anymore.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:48.78.1:00:50.35.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- You don't?  - No.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:51.32.1:00:52.85.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Well. then. why'd you throw out the mug?
Dialogue: 0.1:00:52.95.1:00:54.39.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- What mug?  - Your mug
Dialogue: 0.1:00:54.49.1:00:56.45.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..with the fucking gun on it.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:56.55.1:00:58.59.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- I didn't.  - Yes. you did.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:58.69.1:01:00.43.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I don't know. Maybe it was fucking broken or something.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:00.53.1:01:01.83.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Oh. my God. Why are you lying about it?
Dialogue: 0.1:01:01.93.1:01:03.06.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Okay. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:03.16.1:01:04.63.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I didn't realize the mug meant so much to you.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:04.73.1:01:05.86.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I'm sorry I threw it away.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:05.96.1:01:08.10.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It's obviously not about the fucking mug. Charlie.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:13.94.1:01:15.31.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Ow! Fuck.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:15.41.1:01:16.97.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Fuck. Sorry.  - Charlie. the fuck was that?
Dialogue: 0.1:01:17.08.1:01:19.01.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I'm so sorry. I was just trying to do
Dialogue: 0.1:01:19.11.1:01:20.55.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- your stupid joke thing.  - Just stop.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:20.65.1:01:22.31.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Are you all right?  - Yes. I'm fine. I'm just...
Dialogue: 0.1:01:23.95.1:01:25.32.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Fuck. It's Rachel.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:26.48.1:01:27.45.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Hey.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:28.49.1:01:30.76.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Well. Rachel. you're the maid of honor.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:30.86.1:01:32.39.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..and if you call in the middle of the night
Dialogue: 0.1:01:32.49.1:01:35.23.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..and say you're not coming to the wedding. I mean.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:35.33.1:01:37.03.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..that's not an aggressive move to you?
Dialogue: 0.1:01:37.13.1:01:38.93.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It was barely past 10:00.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:39.03.1:01:41.20.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Still. She's devastated.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:41.30.1:01:43.17.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Well. did she tell you that she had Alice
Dialogue: 0.1:01:43.27.1:01:45.74.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..fire me off that project she. like. begged me
Dialogue: 0.1:01:45.84.1:01:47.21.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..to help her with?
Dialogue: 0.1:01:47.31.1:01:48.87.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..No. no. Why would she do that?
Dialogue: 0.1:01:48.97.1:01:50.07.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Because she's crazy.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:50.17.1:01:51.28.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Stop... stop saying that.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:51.38.1:01:52.98.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Well. how can you even trust her?
Dialogue: 0.1:01:53.08.1:01:54.71.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I mean. 'cause unlike you.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:54.81.1:01:56.25.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..she didn't actually do anything. so...
Dialogue: 0.1:01:56.35.1:01:58.62.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Me? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0.1:01:58.72.1:02:02.32.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yes. You locked a mentally disabled child in a closet.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:02.42.1:02:03.96.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Okay. let's not...  - I never said
Dialogue: 0.1:02:04.06.1:02:05.29.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- he was mentally disabled.  - Yes. you did.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:05.39.1:02:07.66.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You said he was slow. You said he was slow.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:07.76.1:02:09.73.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Please let's not fight. guys.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:09.83.1:02:11.70.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You're being incredibly hypocritical.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:11.80.1:02:13.70.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It was an impulse. Charlie.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:13.80.1:02:15.97.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I didn't plan a cold-blooded murder.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:17.07.1:02:19.67.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Well. she didn't. like... She...
Dialogue: 0.1:02:22.37.1:02:25.48.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..She didn't. like. come up with it on her own.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:26.28.1:02:27.58.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0.1:02:27.68.1:02:30.78.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..'Cause it's like a whole thing in this country. isn't it?
Dialogue: 0.1:02:30.88.1:02:32.32.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I mean. think about it.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:32.42.1:02:34.52.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..If there's a shooting practically every single day.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:34.62.1:02:38.32.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}then imagine how many people must have thought about it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:02:38.42.1:02:42.06.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}Or. like. planned one. Or even got close to it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:02:42.16.1:02:43.23.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}but backed out{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:02:43.33.1:02:45.06.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}or changed their minds for whatever reason.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:02:45.16.1:02:48.30.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}I'm sure there's thousands of people like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:02:48.40.1:02:51.47.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}We just wouldn't know 'cause they would never tell anyone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:02:51.57.1:02:54.67.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}They're just out there. living normal lives.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:02:55.91.1:02:58.11.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}Really could be anyone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:02:58.21.1:03:01.11.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Oh. Here we go. So it's America's fault now?
Dialogue: 0.1:03:01.21.1:03:02.18.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I don't know. I think it's...
Dialogue: 0.1:03:02.28.1:03:03.48.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I do think it's a cultural thing.
Dialogue: 0.1:03:03.58.1:03:05.65.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Oh. please. Look at Mike. he grew up around guns.
Dialogue: 0.1:03:05.75.1:03:06.98.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..and he's terrified of them.
Dialogue: 0.1:03:07.08.1:03:08.72.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I didn't grow up around guns.
Dialogue: 0.1:03:09.92.1:03:10.99.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I thought you said you had an uncle
Dialogue: 0.1:03:11.09.1:03:12.56.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..that owned. like. a bunch of guns.
Dialogue: 0.1:03:12.66.1:03:13.73.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah. because he was a cop.
Dialogue: 0.1:03:13.83.1:03:15.83.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I'm not terrified of them. Why would you even say that?
Dialogue: 0.1:03:15.93.1:03:16.93.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What. so you like guns now?
Dialogue: 0.1:03:17.03.1:03:20.36.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Look. Can I just be completely honest?
Dialogue: 0.1:03:20.47.1:03:22.73.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I was shocked. of course. Just as much as you guys.
Dialogue: 0.1:03:22.84.1:03:24.04.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Like. I...
Dialogue: 0.1:03:24.77.1:03:25.97.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..But...
Dialogue: 0.1:03:26.67.1:03:28.04.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..then we talked. and...
Dialogue: 0.1:03:28.14.1:03:32.71.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..and. uh. she shared some stuff from her past that...
Dialogue: 0.1:03:32.81.1:03:36.15.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I don't know. It just really put it into perspective for me.
